title: Paul Revere
provenance: Reproduced from paper in house of Paul Revere at 19 North Square, Boston.
description: Pillar and arch design. View through an arched opening between columns, to a court with colonnade on either side; beyond, a building with large door and circular spire in five stories. Printed in light and dark browns on medium brown ground. Vertical, a full width, giving nearly two repeats.
name: Sidewall
